{
  "texts": [
    "Each essay received between three and seven ratings from different teachers, with an average of 5.45±0.92 ratings per essay.",
    "We employ the average of the teacher ratings as our ground truth per essay and evaluation criteria.",
    "Essay ScoringTo automatically evaluate student essays based on the ten predefined criteria, we selected different LLMs, to compare the performance of various foundation models.",
    "For closed-source models, we used GPT-3.5 (gpt-3.5-turbo-0125), GPT-4 (gpt-4o-2024-05-13) [37] and o1 (o1-preview) [38] as representative examples.",
    "These GPT models were integrated into our evaluation pipeline via the OpenAI API."
  ]
}